Name},\n   *         to be instantiated\n   * @throws SerializationException if there is no class that corresponds to the\n   *           obfuscated id\n   */\n  String getClassNameForTypeId(String id) throws SerializationException;\n\n  /**\n   * Returns the obfuscated identifier to be used to encode a class in the RPC\n   * wire format.\n   * \n   * @param clazz the class to be transmitted\n   * @return the obfuscated type identifier.\n   * @throws SerializationException\n   */\n  String getTypeIdForClass(Class<?> clazz) throws SerializationException;\n}\n"}], "isError": false, "timestamp": 1777686243083}}
[recv] {"type": "turn_end", "message": {"role": "assistant", "content": [{"type": "thinking", "thinking": "**Considering dependencies and testing**\n\nI’m thinking about using AssertJ and JUnit for testing, but I wonder if the gwt-user dependencies are missing servlet support. I need to write a file that includes the package org_gwtproject.gwt_user, and it looks like I'll need to conduct the tests outside the library package. Also, I should ensure that Base64Utils is public and check the availability of TypeNameObfuscator methods. It’s a bit of a puzzle!", "thinkingSignature": "{\"id\":\"rs_003c2140afb1c8ae0169f556e0156481a19da6c537c5c8cad8\",\"type\":\"reasoning\",\"encrypted_content\":\"gAAAAABp9Vbi1PaZoZWBX1hNAWp7bpnO8XfrfkAFBpOSWhSaSmlPNV3XakUecjG1GM2XHf-fwK77FquUznOVC8pd5fx1Gyd07GNZ5HMt2lM3Ec_bsPIRYa10FeP89soD_2bcrEfnL0xioDGUm5EkBdVa7s5TYTY5G9Yxnv76LgSqMLSwdkFvAW7WWEKoaKDKNnwR0W6IBg8IBuCdadWRb_w9YVmFUaV-x3alLfwOUYh64SMH2tXzZeEyEhk_qF9zPwRPgBmBdBETi1uL6T0TKlsiQTp4xcn9Ocewy79EJ1tZQZicUhT0uM4gNsAYDfyZZ7-OCXeGc0nv1SaAK5OpHfkD9zFCgK_j_3bwu7dNC2ndBoaFIxznrW1PyfMVhBzVAfun3Op57K_NYn1mknY6CfIsAmBZ1m9yn2HO_5FyqFeMlxcL7Ltgj_aXh6gKHpJrbvQCn7ZQ3yBeUextDTDaAmTsr_12Hk2zUh3YEE-GZnA4M8m9qugs_VWsFQwb7NJjB0ogFs8KMnhogI_m7FvcyDLjRs0qAM16ARjjfQUaf6qZRmqWftWWpJCgui0Gvv6kmJOhNALTPWjUDWjO-O684E3CEy3NjthP9ULENJUq3k3K89vmhSpcQ7zWZ22HBXY_WdTlQFOZiSSQXtXf4TYgBwtZvTIXVoXTpcpf4LfS2nEQWv4ONGeHe3ioZkMEJ8_dDTftUZIPOYu1HF4GIPo_h5XcmoI8lOlwhU31YK5fgkD72HP0lwy-Tta-BKdzrGrJe34FyOPjD7-gATVCphjzhtKm-ekeG7bZUAW4dsuhTR5-zJmwJfXkEb5i_lhL6dPMlVfLV6z721wH6q3-yojo1v099UXjg3o_caWvOs7_1caDf6DM2oM-p4S3pVZG9MCaK0S5SQVvx-UKCSOP5zzqC4BjOEOOnxy_jgIY2zwpLfWT-q0sHk-dfdQJuDg87NFUdIBhBAz9QiNFhgqG-BFPa_xU_kLlkNWPv8RBXNgSwGGCD9YTo2pNKOyPov4Zeoxge5lGAWsGqVQtG7BC3mgO1lXDNYUCsFf7g6jNTcVaVawiousRYGjwLRg-v3C4iHrVDuAbRyNkuqlg5IhsPtVL9MIa48lRNj--CMIi4l_XNjpD2usuN5bEpRJBwIfAw0oLPpVMmFT-46QenrljK7F4wlMN01w30KeEsJ9M3aqVDzxNtkYQ-zOXcJKVcE-yKQDXLnVgaF2FEMcdkfSK06elgnsJHzHFin17ObVWJ_Shkcp4qcAqwksybx8=\",\"summary\":[{\"type\":\"su